Definition: the capacity to understand a broad range of topics
Example: a teacher must have a breadth of knowledge of the subject; a man distinguished by the largeness and scope of his views
Synonyms: comprehensiveness, adj, all, inclusive, comprehensive, largeness, large, intelligence, the, capacity, to, understand, a, broad, range, of, topics, teacher, must, have, knowledge, subject, man, distinguished, by, and, scope, his, views
Category: noun.cognition
